    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Crusies incorporating two pans, the upper pan to hold the fuel and wick and the lower pan to serve as a drip catcher.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
